    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee atgreeschahs/ bet ne\npee ta Wiſſu-augstaka/ tee irr ka\nweens wiltigs Stohps/ winzo\nLeel-Kungt krittihs zaar Sohbi-\nnu/ tahs Bahrsibas winzo Mel-\nin deht/ jchi buhs winzo Apmeh-\ndischana Egiptes-Semmê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
